nodes.text: Dice Ibegon was a Force-sensitive Lamproid, a member of the Alliance to Restore the Republic, and the lover of Lak Sivrak. She hoped to convince him to join her in the Alliance. She was a patron of Chalmun's Spaceport Cantina on Tatooine shortly before the Battle of Yavin, where she sat at a table across from a male Pacithhip named Ketwol.
